        <text>
            <body>
                <p>Ego, <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324673" xml:id="d1e130178" corresp="Aimon, abbé de Flavigny (1199)">Haymo dictus abbas
                                <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#284217" xml:id="d1e130180" corresp="abbaye Saint-Pierre et Saint-Prix de Flavigny">Flavin[iacensis]</orgName>
                        </persName>, notum facio presentibus <lb n="2" /> et futuris quod <persName key="d1e11563" xml:id="d1e130185">Petrus, miles de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324424" xml:id="d1e130187" corresp="Alise-Sainte-Reine (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Alisia</placeName>
                        </persName>, dedit et concessit in perpetu<lb n="3" break="no" />am
                        elemosinam ecclesie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e130192" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonten[eti]</orgName> vineam quamdam sitam apud <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324424" xml:id="d1e130196" corresp="Alise-Sainte-Reine (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Alisiam</placeName>
                        <lb n="4" /> et querelam quam eidem ecclesie moverat de quodam prato bona
                        fide guer<lb n="5" break="no" />pivit ; laudans insuper et concedens quod si
                            <persName key="d1e11569" xml:id="d1e130202">Harveus miles de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324452" xml:id="d1e130204" corresp="Fontaines-en-Duesmois (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Fontanis</placeName>
                        </persName>
                        <lb n="6" /> vineam quam habet in supradicta villa prefate ecclesie vendere
                        vel in elemosi<lb n="7" break="no" />nam dare voluerit, quia est de casamento
                        suo, absque sua contradictione libere <lb n="8" /> facere possit. Concessit
                        etiam fratribus ejusdem ecclesie per totam terram <lb n="9" /> juris sui
                        pasturam omnibus animalibus et peccoribus suis usualem et de om<lb n="10" break="no" />ni terra de qua ipsa ecclesia eidem <persName key="d1e11575" xml:id="d1e130217">Petro</persName> decimas tunc debebat quando <lb n="11" /> presens carta facta fuit, ipsas decimas condonavit. Hoc totum
                            lau<lb n="12" break="no" />davit <persName key="d1e11582" xml:id="d1e130224">Regina, uxor sua</persName>, et <persName key="d1e11588" xml:id="d1e130228">Petrus ipsorum filius</persName>.
                        Horum omnium testes <lb n="13" /> sunt <persName key="d1e11594" xml:id="d1e130233">Garnerius de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324480" xml:id="d1e130235" corresp="Mauvilly (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">
                                <foreign>Mavoli</foreign>
                            </placeName>, monachus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#284217" xml:id="d1e130239" corresp="abbaye Saint-Pierre et Saint-Prix de Flavigny">Flavin<supplied>iacensis</supplied>
                            </orgName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e11600" xml:id="d1e130244">Petrus presbiter de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324424" xml:id="d1e130246" corresp="Alise-Sainte-Reine (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Alisia</placeName>
                        </persName>, <lb n="14" />
                        <persName key="d1e30924" xml:id="d1e130250">Harveus miles de
                            Fontanis</persName>, <persName key="d1e11606" xml:id="d1e130254">Gauterius <addName>
                                <foreign>Li Gais</foreign>
                            </addName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e11612" xml:id="d1e130260">Haymo filius
                                <persName key="d1e11619" xml:id="d1e130262">Bero<lb n="15" break="no" />ni</persName>
                        </persName>. Quod totum ut ratum sit, sigilli nostri munimine roboratur,
                            an<lb n="16" break="no" />no verbi incarnati millesimo <num>cc°
                        ii°</num>.</p>
                
